Version 0.3
------------------------------

MAJOR CHANGES

  - Allow for portfolios to be cleaned and completed on a day-to-day basis
  instead of only allowing for a year-to-year

  - New measure of burden based on portfolio size, but assuming some instrument
  or target-based learning mechanism is happening.


MINOR CHANGES

  - Fixed a bug in the production of reports due to country and sector not
  passing correctly as factors.

  - Remove warnings by properly addressing the removal of levels.



Version 0.2.2
------------------------------

Real initial production version with most of the features present.
